data.description: Knock Knock...Who's There? It's the sound of your heart skipping a beat upon pulling up to this cute as a button, fully remodeled and picturesque multi-versatile home! Upon arrival, one of the first attributes you noticed was the sheer size of the lot measuring 67 ft x 163 ft (0.25 acre) complimented by an Oversized Driveway insuring that parking with be no issue for your large family! Once inside this 4 Bedroom, 3 Full Bathroom home, you were greeted to vinyl flooring spanning the living areas and bedrooms. The flexible split floorplan maximizes the usability of the square footage under roof for you and your family’s wants and needs. You then thought “WOW”...there are so many different ways which the generously sized Living Room could be utilized for, including Office & Home Schooling Space perfect for this crazy world we find ourselves living within! You were happy to see the oversized kitchen located within the heart of the home, offered Granite Counter-Tops, Stainless Steel Appliances and plenty of cabinet space. The Master Bedroom houses a huge walk-in closet and Ensuite Full Bathroom. 2 of the other Bedrooms share an updated “Jack n’ Jill” Bathroom with Stand-Up Tiled Shower. The 3rd Bathroom is located right off the kitchen, convenient for both Guests along with the location of the 4th and final Bedroom. The rear of the home adorns a covered deck/patio area leading to a covered and enclosed Utility Closet housing space for the Brand new Washer & Dryer, thats included. Have plans for a pool? Space to install your dream pool will be no issue whatsoever, as your new backyard is a blank canvas awaiting your inspiration!
